  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\"><img alt=\"Volantis.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e7/Volantis.svg/50px-Volantis.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e7/Volantis.svg/75px-Volantis.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e7/Volantis.svg/100px-Volantis.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Nysseos Qoheros</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\"><img alt=\"Volantis.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e7/Volantis.svg/50px-Volantis.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e7/Volantis.svg/75px-Volantis.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e7/Volantis.svg/100px-Volantis.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Nysseos Qoheros</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantene</a> and the author of <i><a href=\"/index.php/Journals\" title=\"Journals\">Journals</a></i>. Among the events he reports the fate of Triarch <a href=\"/index.php/Horonno\" title=\"Horonno\">Horonno</a>, who tried to declare himself triarch for life and was executed for it.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nysseos_Qoheros&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Free Cities: Volantis.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403121213\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.095 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.370 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 383/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10374/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4351/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 327/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 622/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.250/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.29 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  361.915      1 -total\n 97.89%  3